-streamers/streamer-d4vd-becomes-center-of-alleged-1-2m-insider-betting-scandal-involving-a-google-engineer/articleshow/131377440.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/streamer-d4vd-becomes-center-of-alleged-1-2m-insider-betting-scandal-involving-a-google-engineer/articleshow/131377440.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T00:51:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131377431,imgsize-474224.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google engineer arrested after turning $1,000 bet on jailed singer D4vd into $1.2 million]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131376524.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/google-engineer-arrested-after-turning-1000-bet-on-jailed-singer-d4vd-into-1-2-million-released-on-2-25-million-bond/articleshow/131376524.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/google-engineer-arrested-after-turning-1000-bet-on-jailed-singer-d4vd-into-1-2-million-released-on-2-25-million-bond/articleshow/131376524.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T00:49:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131377417,imgsize-165060.cms"/></item></channel></rss>